org.sql: SELECT queries.* FROM queries LEFT OUTER JOIN projects ON queries.project_id = projects.id WHERE queries.type IN ('TimeEntryQuery') AND (queries.project_id IS NULL OR projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'time_tracking') IS NOT NULL) AND (queries.visibility <> 0 OR queries.user_id = 1) AND queries.project_id IS NULL ORDER BY queries.name ASC, queries.id ASC
